Ing '''University of the Cordilleras''', a sadiang '''Baguio Colleges Foundation (BCF)''', metung yang privadung universidad king [[Baguio Lakanbalen]], [[Filipinas]]. Kilala re ing universidad a Sentru ning Pamagaral king Pangulu (''Center of Education in the North'') uling atiu iti king [[Baguio Lakanbalen]], metung a ciudad o lakanbalen king pangulu nang dake ning Filipinas. <ref name=profile>Official press release, University of the Cordilleras. 2007.</ref> Malapit ya king palengki ning lakanbalen ing universidad, ampo king [[Baguio Cathedral|Our Lady of Atonement Church (Baguio Cathedral)]], ampo reng hotel, restoran, ampong mall.<ref name=profile>Official press release, University of the Cordilleras. 2007.</ref>

